      "description": "$19,500 - Honest driver in fair overall condition with the expected wear that comes from age and regular use. It presents decently enough for weekend drives or local events, but it does show noticeable cosmetic blemishes, aging trim, and a generally used appearance inside and out. The interior is complete and usable, though it has clear signs of wear, and buyers should expect an older car that feels more driver-quality than show-quality. A solid choice for someone who wants an enjoyable, presentable car without paying for a fully sorted top-tier example.",
