    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this car is a great option for someone who wants an affordable runabout, a project, or a handy parts car. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be a smart buy.",
