    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone wanting an affordable driver or light project. This car shows cosmetic wear consistent with age, but it presents as a complete, usable package with a drivetrain that pulls through the rev range and a chassis that still feels planted. The engine starts, runs, and settles into a steady idle, and the transmission does its job as it should. A good candidate for a commuter, backup car, or weekend wrenching platform with plenty of life left for the next owner willing to tidy the details. If you want something inexpensive, mechanically straightforward, and ready to put to work, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
